fr.curie.cd2sbgnml.model

Class LinkModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.curie.cd2sbgnml.model.LinkModel

  • public class LinkModel
extends Object
    A geometric link with more information about the reaction it is involved in, like its source and target elements, its style and its class (determining arrow shapes).

        Merge 2 links together, and create a new LinkModel as a result. It is assumed that data are consistent between the 2 merged links (same style, end of the first is more or less the same as start of the 2nd, same middle element...)
